description: BMO US Preferred Share Hedged to CAD Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent, the performance of the Solactive US Preferred Share Select Hedged to CAD Index (NTR), net of expenses. The ETF invests in and holds the Constituent Securities of the Index in the same proportion as they are reflected in the Index. The U.S. currency exposure is hedged back to Canadian dollars. ZHP is a fund of fund; the management fees charged are reduced by those accrued in the underlying funds.
name: BMO US Preferred Share Hedged to CAD Index ETF
